// Embeds mft_reader.manifest into the executable as resource type 24
// (RT_MANIFEST), id 1 (CREATEPROCESS_MANIFEST_RESOURCE_ID). This is what
// makes Windows show the UAC elevation prompt automatically whenever the
// .exe is launched, regardless of how it's started (double-click, cmd,
// Explorer, etc.) - no need to manually "Run as administrator".
1 24 "mft_reader.manifest"
